<paragraph blockId="3.[151,1405,1716,1739]" box="[151,1405,1716,1739]" pageId="3" pageNumber="50">
Lophoziae 
<emphasis box="[270,1398,1716,1739]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="50">primo adspectu maxime simile, sed gemmis rubellis usque ad aurantiacis et guttis olei flavis, permanentis</emphasis>
